01:05:25,187 --> 01:05:29,214
<i>Just one more killing, Frankie,</i>
<i>then you're through.</i>

648
01:05:29,325 --> 01:05:33,284
<i>One more to die,</i>
<i>and then you won't have to be alone.</i>

649
01:05:44,640 --> 01:05:47,006
<i>You know, Frankie,</i>
<i>you're really a very attractive guy.</i>

650
01:05:47,109 --> 01:05:49,077
<i>How come you're not married?</i>

651
01:05:49,178 --> 01:05:52,511
<i>What you probably need is a girl...</i>

652
01:05:52,615 --> 01:05:54,583
<i>or someone.</i>

653
01:05:54,684 --> 01:05:57,482
<i>You know, someone</i>
<i>that you could feel good with.</i>

654
01:05:57,586 --> 01:06:00,111
<i>Someone who could</i>
<i>make you feel at home.</i>

655
01:06:31,253 --> 01:06:34,450
- Frankie.
- Lori, I-I wanna talk to you.

656
01:06:34,557 --> 01:06:38,084
Oh, I-I'm terribly sorry, Frank.
It's so early, and I --

657
01:06:38,194 --> 01:06:40,128
It's -- It's important.

658
01:06:40,229 --> 01:06:43,630
You know, what we said
the other night about --

659
01:06:43,733 --> 01:06:46,998
what you told me about --
about needing somebody.

660
01:06:47,103 --> 01:06:50,095
Well, I -- I've been thinking about it,
and you were right.

661
01:06:51,540 --> 01:06:53,565
I do need somebody.

662
01:06:53,676 --> 01:06:56,804
What I'm trying to say is this:

663
01:06:56,912 --> 01:06:59,676
Lori, I need you.

664
01:06:59,782 --> 01:07:02,979
- <i>Frank, I'm sorry</i>--
- <i>Lori, sweetheart, have you got</i>--

665
01:07:03,085 --> 01:07:04,985
Hello, Frank.

666
01:07:06,922 --> 01:07:11,359
- What the hell is this?
- I'm -- I'm terribly sorry, Frankie.

667
01:07:12,661 --> 01:07:14,561
You must have misunderstood.

668
01:07:14,663 --> 01:07:16,631
What?

669
01:07:16,732 --> 01:07:19,530
<i>It's just that you were so lonely.</i>

670
01:07:19,635 --> 01:07:22,126
- <i>I just thought</i>--
- You thought what?

671
01:07:22,238 --> 01:07:24,206
- <i>Well, you really ought to call</i>--
- Shut up!

672
01:07:26,108 --> 01:07:28,008
What?

673
01:07:29,512 --> 01:07:31,844
- That --
- Never mind. Never mind.

674
01:07:33,049 --> 01:07:35,017
I understand.

675
01:07:35,117 --> 01:07:37,051
Merry Christmas.

676
01:07:41,023 --> 01:07:43,150
<i>Watch it, Frankie. Danger signals.</i>

677
01:07:43,259 --> 01:07:46,387
<i>Like electric current, like lightning,</i>
<i>like fire in the night...</i>

678
01:07:46,495 --> 01:07:48,861
<i>and sirens screaming in your head.</i>

679
01:07:48,964 --> 01:07:51,956
<i>Don't think. Don't remember.</i>
<i>Don't look ahead.</i>

680
01:07:52,068 --> 01:07:54,434
<i>Concentrate.</i>

681
01:07:54,537 --> 01:07:56,971
<i>You have a job to do,</i>
<i>and you're an expert.</i>

682
01:07:57,073 --> 01:07:59,837
<i>A killer who doesn't kill</i>
<i>gets killed.</i>

683
01:12:58,774 --> 01:13:02,642
<i>One last contact</i>-- <i>to pick up your money.</i>

684
01:13:02,745 --> 01:13:05,714
<i>Only a few minutes,</i>
<i>and then you'll be alone again...</i>

685
01:13:05,814 --> 01:13:09,875
<i>the way you were meant to be,</i>
<i>the way you like it.</i>

686
01:13:25,634 --> 01:13:27,602
This is Cleveland.

687
01:16:44,266 --> 01:16:46,962
<i>"God moves in mysterious ways,"they said.</i>

688
01:16:47,069 --> 01:16:50,596
<i>Maybe he is on your side,</i>
<i>the way it all worked out.</i>

689
01:16:50,706 --> 01:16:52,970
<i>Remembering other Christmases...</i>

690
01:16:53,075 --> 01:16:56,875
<i>wishing for something,</i>
<i>something important, something special.</i>

691
01:16:56,979 --> 01:17:00,107
<i>And this is it,</i>
<i>baby boy Frankie Bono.</i>

692
01:17:00,215 --> 01:17:02,547
<i>You're alone now. All alone.</i>

693
01:17:03,785 --> 01:17:05,776
<i>The scream is dead.</i>

694
01:17:05,887 --> 01:17:08,549
<i>There's no pain.</i>
<i>You're home again.</i>

695
01:17:08,657 --> 01:17:11,990
<i>Back in the cold, black silence.</i>
